  "name": "RPlog_A_Fallen_Comrade",
  "title": "A Fallen Comrade",
  "summary": "On a deep-space security sweep among a star's small moons, New Republic Ghost Squadron pilots Raxis L'ygr (callsign Raptor) and Lance Corbet (callsign Wildman) detect a lone TIE fighter lurking near a damaged Imperial cruiser, the HIMS Reaper. The Imperial pilot, Wolf, deliberately lures the two X-wings into a dogfight to draw them away from his crippled ship. In the exchange Wolf disables Lance's fighter and damages Raxis's, forcing Raxis to limp into hyperspace to summon backup while his wingman is left adrift. Wolf reports his prize, and the Reaper jumps in to scoop up the disabled X-wing and capture Lance before vanishing into hyperspace, leaving Raxis the grim duty of carrying word of the loss home.",
